metadata.name: THE TOKYBiRD PENGUIN #1
metadata.description:
THE TOKYBiRDS: PENGUINS is a collection of 3 000 randomly created Penguins drawn by swiss Artist BRAINFART.
The Penguins are the guardians of the MYTOKYBiRD brand and the community. They bring light into the darkness and conjure a smile on sad faces. Because no matter how big our problems in the world are, there is always a TOKYBiRD that helps to support the people and organizations that do good.
After the hatch, each single TOKYBiRD PENGUIN will support Fund The Planet and protects 5sqm of rainforest in Peru. 

See it here https://explorer.fundtheplanet.net/0x53e025a170693aac17da12e3773d6d15be78e680
With every sale, we will donate a part of the proceeds to good causes. Visit our Discord to see where our donations are going.
